# A `.pubignore` overrides the `.gitignore` in the SAME directory for `pub
# publish` (dart.dev/go/pubignore). So this file must mirror the root
# `.gitignore` patterns, otherwise build output, IDE files, etc. leak into the
# published archive. Keep it in sync with `.gitignore`.

# --- mirror of .gitignore ---
# Miscellaneous
*.class
*.log
*.pyc
*.swp
.DS_Store
.atom/
.buildlog/
.history
.svn/

# IntelliJ related
*.iml
*.ipr
*.iws
.idea/

# Flutter/Dart/Pub related
/pubspec.lock
**/doc/api/
.dart_tool/
.packages
build/

# --- package-specific exclusions ---
# Internal quality-audit / orientation doc — kept in the repo, not shipped.
PROJECT_OVERVIEW.md
